  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Yllas Saaga Apartments are self-catering apartments within walking distance of the local mini-market. All apartments are equipped with a small kitchenette, giving you the option to dine in or check out the local restaurants in the village</p>
<p>Optional pre-bookable half board option is also available in the <a data-udi="umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446}" title="Yllas Saaga Spa Hotel">Ylläs Saaga Hotel</a> (up to a 300 metre walk). The breakfast is buffet style with hot and cold options, served from 7am - 10am. Dinner is three courses with a choice of main, available from 6pm - 7.30pm. </p>
<p>Guests can receive a 30% discount for the <span>à la carte restaurant. Please inform the reception by 6pm the day before. Please note that the à la carte restaurant is not guaranteed to be open all season.</span></p>
<p>Festive Feast included for all guests during December, for a Christmas celebration, games. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
