  <description><![CDATA[<p>Ylläs Saaga Apartments have a convenience slope side location, making these apartments virtually ski in, ski out. Plus there are wonderful views as far as the eye can see. admire the <span>fell or the snow covered horizon.</span> The apartments are on the Ylläsjarvi side of the fell, a short bus ride from the <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Akaslompolo</a> centre, plus the ski lifts, ski school meeting place and ski hire shop are just next door.</p>
<h2>Slope side apartments</h2>
<p>Located on the Ylläsjarvi side of the fell, the Saaga Apartments are ideal for keen skiers and boarders, as the slopes and ski lifts are a snowballs throw away - making it incredibly easy to get on and off the piste each day. An added benefit being the ski school meeting point and ski hire shop are conveniently located next door. Lapland offers a unique skiing experience as the slopes are floodlit, allowing you to ski on the gentle slopes from sunrise to sunset - even when there are limited daylight hours. </p>
<h2>Modern and spacious</h2>
<p>The apartments are modern and spacious, furnished in a contemporary Nordic style, with all the features needed for a week in Lapland including a TV, kitchen, drying cabinet and a sauna. The Saaga apartments are set out across different blocks, with one block being connected to the hotel and another block being around 300 metres from the hotel.</p>
<p>The apartments form part of the resort with the <a data-udi="umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446}" title="Yllas Saaga Spa Hotel">Ylläs Saaga Hotel</a>. Pre-book the optional 'Spa Package' where you can enjoy the excellent spa facilities,<span> including an indoor swimming pool, sauna, steam room and hot tub for the duration of your stay (pre-book or pay locally). </span></p>
<h2>Eat in or dine out</h2>
<p>The apartments are on a self-catering basis, with a equipped kitchen it is easy to cook tasty meals from the comfort of your apartment. In addition to cafes, shops, and restaurants, there is a well-stocked supermarket in the village centre. There is also the option to upgrade to half board in the <a data-udi="umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446}" title="Yllas Saaga Spa Hotel">Ylläs Saaga Hotel</a> (approx. 150 metre walk), you can enjoy a breakfast buffet with hot and cold options, and a three course dinner each day.</p>]]></description>
