  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One Bedroom Apartments </strong>are around 43m², sleeping one to four people. The apartments have one twin bedroom and a double sofa bed in the open plan living room and kitchen.</p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom Apartment</strong> are around 62m², sleeping two to six people. The apartments have two twin bedrooms and a double sofa bed in the open plan living room and kitchen.</p>
<p>There is a mid-week clean with towel and linen change. End of stay cleaning is included.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Drying closet</li>
<li>TV </li>
<li>Radio</li>
<li>Fully equipped kitchen with oven, microwave, dishwasher, coffee-maker, grill and toaster</li>
<li>Shower and WC</li>
<li>One linen and towel set included, per person per week</li>
<li>Final clean included </li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi access in the hotel reception</li>
<li>Apartments which are not connected to the main building have Wi-Fi. Apartments connected to the hotel access have internet access via a cable suitable for laptops (free Wi-Fi in the lobby).</li>
</ul>
<p>The Saaga Apartments will always try to situate our guests in the block connected to the hotel, however guests may also be located in nearby apartment blocks which are not directly connected to the hotel and are up to a 300 metre walk away.</p>
<p>For hotel rooms check out the <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Ylläs Saaga Hotel</a>. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
